      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense for the paper. To make my section on the 'scientific' side more detailed, could you go deeper into what they actually believed about the specific physiological or mental differences between these groups? Like, what were the actual claims they were making about the intellectual capacity or 'civilizational potential' of different races to back up their hierarchy?",
